{
  "stem": "20609.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "All of a sudden, the father came in and that's when-- when they took me out of that class and put me in a Jewish school.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And to this day, I'm saying, why wasn't that a signal for my parents to get out of Germany?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I mean, they should have known at that time-- this was '34, '35.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My mother had a brother in the United States who could have been-- well, you can't talk about spilled milk.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So the other thing I-- I-- I-- was-- I belonged to [INAUDIBLE], the sports club, as a soccer player.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the occasion for me to play soccer was so rare because at the German-- if the Germans decided to close down the-- the-- the stadium for a day and it-- it really wasn't-- I mean, it wasn't really a stadium.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was one of the worst places.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It only had to goal posts and-- and there was some grass in it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you know, there was no maintenance whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were never-- hardly ever allowed to play.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and many times, I used to smuggle myself into these pools, you know, swimming pools.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you know, you have to take a shower first.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was circumcised so it wasn't-- so I had to always, like, walk through with the towel in front of me so nobody could spot me till I put my trunks on and jump in the pool.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then you couldn't go to a movie.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we didn't have a radio anymore, they were impounded.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we didn't have-- well, cars we never had anyway, so it didn't-- didn't-- was no big deal.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But it-- it started little by little getting worse.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
